<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <title>Cab Clique</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Carter+One&family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #c6f1e7, #e1f7d5);
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.5rem 5%;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .logo-container {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.8rem;
    }
    
    .logo-container img {
      height: 45px;
    }

    .cab-clique {
      font-family: 'Carter One', cursive;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: #2c3e50;
      animation: fadeDown 1s ease-in-out;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #2c3e50;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #0077ff;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .button-10 {
      padding: 8px 18px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #56ccf2, #2f80ed);
      color: white;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }

    .button-10:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #2f80ed, #56ccf2);
    }

    .main-content {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 2rem;
      padding: 2rem 5%;
    }

    .text-content {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 280px;
      animation: fadeInLeft 1s ease-in-out;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .find {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #1f2937;
    }

    .book {
      color: #e67e22;
    }

    .easily {
      color: #0077ff;
    }

    .with-vitians span:last-child {
      color: #0077ff;
    }

    .image-15-icon {
      flex: 1;
      max-width: 500px;
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 16px;
      animation: fadeInRight 1.5s ease-in-out;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding: 1rem 5%;
      background-color: #ffffffcc;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    footer a {
      color: #2c3e50;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-left: 1rem;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      color: #0077ff;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @keyframes fadeInLeft {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(-50px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
      }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInRight {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(50px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
      }
    }

    @keyframes fadeDown {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(-30px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    /* ----------- Responsive Design ----------- */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      header {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      nav {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 0.5rem;
      }

      .main-content {
        flex-direction: column-reverse;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .cab-clique {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .tagline {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      footer {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      footer a {
        margin-left: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="logo-container">
      <img src="styles/pngwing.com.png" alt="Cab Clique Logo" />
      <div class="cab-clique">CAB CLIQUE</div>
    </div>
    <nav>
      <!-- <a href="#">Create Group</a> -->
      <!-- The Button -->
<a href="#" onclick="openGuide()" style="cursor: pointer; ">New Here?</a>

<!-- The Guide Modal -->
<div id="guideModal" style="display:none; position:fixed; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.6); z-index:1000;">
  <div style="background:white; padding:20px; max-width:600px; margin:8% auto; border-radius:10px; position:relative; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
    <span onclick="closeGuide()" style="position:absolute; top:10px; right:15px; cursor:pointer; font-size:24px; font-weight: bold;">&times;</span>
    <h2 style="margin-top:0;">How to Use Cab Clique</h2>
    <p>Welcome to Cab Clique! Here’s how you can use the site after login:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Join a Group:</strong> Find a group going your way and send a message with your contact details and a message to the group uploader.</li>
      <li><strong>Group Owner:</strong> If you created a group, check your message box to see join requests from other students. You can contact them to coordinate rides.</li>
      <li><strong>Create a Group:</strong> If no suitable group exists, create your own and share your ride details.</li>
      <li><strong>View Profiles:</strong> Click on any username to see the profile/about section of the person who uploaded the group.</li>
      <li><strong>Edit Profile:</strong> You can update your own profile information in the profile section.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Enjoy hassle-free shared rides and save on travel costs!</p>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  function openGuide() {
    document.getElementById('guideModal').style.display = 'block';
  }
  
  function closeGuide() {
    document.getElementById('guideModal').style.display = 'none';
  }
</script>

     
      <button id="loginButton" class="button-10">Login / Sign Up</button>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="main-content">
    <div class="text-content">
  <div class="tagline" style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.4; color: #333;">
    <span class="find" style="color: #007bff;">Share</span> your ride, 
    <span class="book" style="color: #28a745;">split the cost</span> <br>
    <span class="easily" style="color: #ff5722;">smarter travel</span> for Vitian's
  </div>
  <p class="with-vitians" style="margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.2rem; color: #555;">
    <span class="find" style="font-weight: 600; color: #007bff;">With</span> 
    <span style="font-style: italic;">Vitian’s</span>
  </p>
</div>

    <img class="image-15-icon" src="styles/ChatGPT Image Jun 3, 2025, 12_10_36 PM.png" alt="Cab Service Illustration" />
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div>© 2025 Cab Clique. All rights reserved.</div>
    <div>
      <a href="#">Privacy</a>
      <a href="#">Terms</a>
      <a href="#">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.getElementById("loginButton").addEventListener("click", function () {
      window.location.href = "/login";
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
